org.gvsig.normalization.patterns
Class Element

java.lang.Object
  org.gvsig.normalization.patterns.Element
All Implemented Interfaces:
GeocodingPersistence
public class Element
extends java.lang.Object
implements GeocodingPersistence

Class Element. This class are the all elements that they make the pattern. Each element defines one new field in final table. The attributes of each element are: - (_fieldname) Name of the new field - (_fieldtype) Type of the new field (String, Integer, Decimal or Date) - (_fieldwith) Number of position to split the main string. If this value is zero the split process will be via separators - (_fieldseparator) separators between fields - (infieldseparators) special characters within one substring (thousand character, decimal character, text characters) - (_importfield) this boolean defines if this new field will be normalized
